        <abstract> 
<p>Sends copy of last edition of <hi rend="italic">Origin</hi>.</p> 
            <p>Respecting AH’s theory that acceleration of growth produces new characters, urges AH to examine decapods that do and do not pass through zoea stage. Believes there are no marked differences between them.</p>
